      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:3:3:24:13",
      "text": [
        " سَأَلْتُهُ عَنِ الْجَرِيدَةِ تُوضَعُ مِنْ دُونِ الثِّيَابِ أَوْ مِنْ فَوْقِهَا قَالَ فَوْقَ الْقَمِيصِ وَ دُونَ الْخَاصِرَةِ فَسَأَلْتُهُ مِنْ أَيِّ جَانِبٍ فَقَالَ مِنَ الْجَانِبِ الْأَيْمَنِ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from Ibn Abu Umeyr, from Jameel who said, ",
          "‘I asked him<sup>asws</sup> about the twig to be placed below the cloth (shroud), or from above it?’ He<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘Above the shirt and below the loins’. So I asked him<sup>asws</sup>, ‘From which side?’ So he<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘On the right side’."
        ]
      }
    },
